{"tid":2393783,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"無線翻拍《十月初五的月光》 傳地點由澳門改成流浮山","createTime":"2021-02-03T17:15:20.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-04T10:05:53.000Z","uid":28114,"like":9,"dislike":146,"uniUserReply":77,"replies":[{"pid":"96b0b88ed5a4afe114a4febb58d84abf73c24317","tid":2393783,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T17:15:20.000Z","msg":"無線近日為《十月初五的月光》2021 炒冷飯版開鏡，角色改頭換面，有傳拍攝地點由澳門改成流浮山。孝子胡鴻鈞 Pro Max 飾演張智霖嘅經典角色「初哥哥」，君好就係何依婷。初哥哥嘅情敵就係馬子仁飾演嘅司徒禮信。<br />\n<br />\nCaptain Nancy 力保 Q 姨一角失敗，新版由米雪飾演，佢知己「全海景」就係石修。曼娜姐飾演嘅經典角色、最講道理嘅萬朱莎華就係姚嘉妮，霸氣度爭好遠喎！網民就大潑冷水，話呢個新版完全「毀童年」「古裝都話，翻拍時裝劇做乜」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CE5yOUG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCE5yOUG.jpg&h=b50dfac8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/169934393078433/posts/4990140871057737/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F169934393078433%2Fposts%2F4990140871057737%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=f02Xtm2mX5FaAGCExHUdjQomF%2BlBZ%2FxAFwVMru4Rc7Q%3D&h=338fb2cc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/169934393078433/posts/4990140871057737/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"6fa65b542edf66d19308268916f755d7b7ba8189","tid":2393783,"uid":28114,"like":263,"dislike":0,"score":263,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T17:15:46.000Z","msg":"流浮刀手的血光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bed444b336961b9706ff9f20d722fcae1c04d08d","tid":2393783,"uid":92299,"like":207,"dislike":3,"score":204,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T17:17:14.000Z","msg":"七月廿二的刀手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94ddc09385ccb812956bddb65bbbceb5c6aea5fd","tid":2393783,"uid":196329,"like":147,"dislike":2,"score":145,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T17:18:34.000Z","msg":"陳蔓娜粒icon<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal